</pre>

See `enabled_background.html`

h4. Scrolling in a container

<pre><img class="lazy" data-original="img/example.jpg" width="765" height="574"></pre>

<pre>
#container {
    height: 600px;
    overflow: scroll;
}
</pre>

<pre>
$("img.lazy").lazyload({         
    effect : "fadeIn",
    container: $("#container")
